---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'

---

<Layout title='Reza Kargar | Home'>
  <main>
    <div class='flex flex-col-reverse md:items-start items-center justify-center md:flex-row'>
      <div class='w-9/12 text-white md:w-[450px]'>
        <h1 class='glitch mb-1 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl'>
          Reza Kargar
        </h1>
        <h2 class='glitch mt-2 text-lg'>Software Engineer at
          <a
            href='https://www.digikala.com'
            target='_blank'
            class='rounded-lg p-1 hover:bg-primary-red hover:text-gray-900 text-primary-red'>
            Digikala.com
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class='mt-4 text-left'>
          <div class="leading-relaxed">
            <p>Hey there, welcome to my corner of the web! I'm just your friendly neighborhood <span class="text-primary-purple">software engineer</span> 😁✌️,
               living and breathing all things tech and programming.
               When I'm not knee-deep in code, you'll probably catch me chilling out with a movie or strolling around,
               lost in an audiobook, podcast, or jamming out to my favorite tunes. 🚶🎧</p>
            <br />
            <p>Now, let's talk fandoms – I'm a certified <span  class="text-primary-purple">Potterhead</span> ⚡️,
              a BBC <span class="text-primary-orange">Sherlock</span> fanatic 🕵️‍♂️,
              and don't even get me started on Marvel, especially <span class="text-primary-red">Spider-Man</span> 🕷️ – he's my guy!</p>
            <p>Oh, and if you're wondering about my favorite colors, it's gotta be
              <span class="text-primary-purple">purple</span> and <span class="text-primary-orange">orange</span>, no contest.</p>
            <br />
            <p>And hey, let's bond over some serious stuff – like <span class="text-yellow-400">ice cream</span>.🍦
              Seriously, nothing beats a scoop (or three) of pure bliss. So, if you're as passionate about ice cream as I am,
              we're practically destined to be best buds. Grab a spoon, let's dive in, and let the good times roll! 🎉</p>
          </div>         
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        id='pfp-1'
        class='mb-10 ml-0 w-60 rounded-md md:mb-0 md:ml-10 md:h-[240px] md:w-[240px]'
        src='https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29206777?v=4'
        alt='Reza Kargar'
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
